// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5891 — Mass File Rename (incransom)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: caec70f1-ca4b-54ad-850c-16413a22aa43

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
